<node TEXT="16. &#x201c;The Recursive Girl&#x201d;&#xa;Haliechuck: This is the point where the characters explain what they&#x2019;ve learned. Vivian says she was in love with David and they lost their love and she was able to keep going, and she was able to keep their love with her wherever they went. This is a counterpoint to David: She was able to take his pain and that experience made her life richer." FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1822790379" CREATED="1548237278251" MODIFIED="1548237279325">
