<node TEXT="18. &#x201c;Lights Go Up&#x201d;&#xa;Haliechuck: David&#x2019;s now an older person. He&#x2019;s glad it happened and he wants to do it again. David goes back to the factory, and it&#x2019;s a second chance. He&#x2019;s learned what he needs to learn; he&#x2019;s glad with his experiences. And he goes back and gets to live it again. The record sort of resets." FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1080872588" CREATED="1548237298811" MODIFIED="1548237299725">
